。遲下有錢到買起香港了。"},{"pid":"1fc1f8151edd6a3d6a3b7cc1f74a5ee62ca1c30c","tid":477850,"uid":8257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T02:11:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁渣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 試玩左高地價十年八年就謝左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n香港玩左成40年都未死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b1babc372966b11499688f165286d0598e4f112","tid":477850,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T02:13:34.000Z","msg":"又燈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9b1873c58310a33e26bcdce19abbe196cc55db3","tid":477850,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T02:14:21.000Z","msg":"深圳怎麼了？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n超越香港未?"},{"pid":"e8018d8e52f919fdc5cab684bd8b3125ae8830cf","tid":477850,"uid":38671,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T02:16:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>連登數據，又要燈爆支那。遲下有錢到買起香港了。</blockquote><br />\n有線中國組又關連登事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}